(1, 'about', 'ABOUT US Lt', 'ABOUT US', 'ABOUT US Ru', 'Our bank is one of the largest international financial organizations. We serve over 40 million customers worldwide. We operate in four main business areas: Retail banking and asset management (Retail Banking and Wealth Management), Commercial banking (Commercial Banking), Banking services in global markets (Avrora Capital Bank and Markets), as well as Global management of large private capital (Avrora Capital Bank). Our offices are located in many countries and territories of Europe, Asia, the Middle East, North Africa, as well as North and Latin America. Lt', 'Our bank is one of the largest international financial organizations. We serve over 40 million customers worldwide. We operate in four main business areas: Retail banking and asset management (Retail Banking and Wealth Management), Commercial banking (Commercial Banking), Banking services in global markets (Avrora Capital Bank and Markets), as well as Global management of large private capital (Avrora Capital Bank). Our offices are located in many countries and territories of Europe, Asia, the Middle East, North Africa, as well as North and Latin America.', 'Ru Our bank is one of the largest international financial organizations. We serve over 40 million customers worldwide. We operate in four main business areas: Retail banking and asset management (Retail Banking and Wealth Management), Commercial banking (Commercial Banking), Banking services in global markets (Avrora Capital Bank and Markets), as well as Global management of large private capital (Avrora Capital Bank). Our offices are located in many countries and territories of Europe, Asia, the Middle East, North Africa, as well as North and Latin America.', '<div class=\"block-info\">\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__title\">Lt We strive to provide:</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">Application of the principles of equality and justice in relation to employees;</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">Employee development for the implementation of current and future business goals;</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">Afe working conditions;</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">An atmosphere of openness in the work team;</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">Election and promotion of employees based on their qualifications and achievements;</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">Assessment and remuneration of employees in accordance with their skills and performance;</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">Creating a work environment conducive to achieving business goals;</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">The formation of an internal culture that supports initiative and innovation;</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">Opportunities for optimal realization of the professional potential of employees;</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">Formation of an employee development program to meet business needs;</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">Teamwork and team integration support</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">To implement the growth strategy, Avrora Capital Bank in Russia is looking for loyal employees who are aware of the responsibility for the company\'s image and the quality of the products and services provided.</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n\r\n				<div class=\"block-info\">\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__title\">Jobs</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">There are currently no open vacancies.</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">Avrora Capital Bank is based on the idea of creating a local bank to solve global financial problems. The first Avrora Capital Bank branch opened in Hong Kong in March 1865. Now we are one of the largest international financial organizations.</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n\r\n				<div class=\"block-info\">\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__title\">Single European Register</p>\r\n					<p class=\"block-info__text\">Our company has been included in the unified register of Europe. Number